column4: U.S. court rules Qualcomm must license technology to rivals
column5: A U.S. federal judge ruled on Tuesday that chip seller Qualcomm Inc  must license some of its technology to competitors such as Intel Corp .

column4: UPDATE 2-U.S. court rules Qualcomm must license technology to rivals
column5: Nov 6 A U.S. federal judge ruled on Tuesday that chip seller Qualcomm Inc must license some of its technology to competitors such as Intel Corp.

column4: Qualcomm dealt setback in case brought by U.S. trade regulator
column5: Nov 6 Mobile chip firm Qualcomm Inc suffered a setback in an antitrust brought against by the U.S. Federal Trade Commission on Tuesday when a judge sided with trade regulators on a motion for partial summary judgment.
